quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  21,45,keh do ke mein tum ko hukum khuda ke mutabiq nasiyaat karta hon. aur behroon kojb nasiyaat ki jaye to woh pukaar kar suntay hi nahi
  21,46,aur agar un ko tumahray perwar-digaar ka thora sa azaab bhi puhanche to kehnay lagen ke haae kam bakhti hum be shak sitamgar they
  21,47,aur hum qayamat ke din insaaf ki traazo khari karen ge to kisi shakhs ki zara bhi haq talfi nah ki jaye gi. aur agar rai ke danay ke barabar bhi ( kisi ka amal ) hoga to hum is ko la hazir karen ge. aur hum hisaab karne ko kaafi hain
  21,48,aur hum ne moose aur Haroon ko ( hadaayat aur gumraahi mein ) farq kar dainay wali aur ( srtapa ) roshni aur nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) ataa ki ( yani ) parhaiz gaaron ke liye
  21,49,jo ban dekhe apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain aur qayamat ka bhi khauf rakhtay hain
  21,50,yeh mubarak nasiyaat hai jisay hum ne nazil farmaya hai tokiya tum is se inkaar karte ho ?
  21,51,aur hum ne ibrahim ko pehlay hi se hadaayat di thi aur hum un ke haal se waaqif they
  21,52,jab unhon ne apne baap aur apni qoum ke logon se kaha yehkiya moorten hain jin ( ki parastish ) par tum mutakif (o qaa-im ) ho ?
  21,53,woh kehnay lagey ke hum ne apne baap dada ko un ki parastish karte dekha hai
  21,54,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ke tum bhi ( gumraah ho ) aur tumahray baap dada bhi Sarih gumraahi mein parre rahay
  21,55,woh bolaykiya tum hamaray paas ( waqai ) haq laaye ho ya ( hum se ) khail ( ki baatein ) karte ho ?
  21,56,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ( nahi ) balkay tumhara perwar-digaar asmano aur zameen ka perwar-digaar hai jis ne un ko pedakiya hai. aur mein is ( baat ) ka gawah ( aur isi ka qaail ) hon
  21,57,aur khuda ki qasam jab tum peeth phair kar chalay jao ge to mein tumahray buton se aik chaal chaloon ga
